  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK745">
<l>koḷaṟkaritāyk koṇṭakūḻt tāki yakattār</l>
<l>nilaikkeḷitā nīra taraṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A fort is that which cannot be captured, which abounds in suitable provisions, and affords a position of easy defence to its inmates.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
